{"tid":2432243,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"根本緬甸已經是六四事件了，但國際間（聯合國）仍然係食花生心態","createTime":"2021-03-04T07:28:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-04T08:33:48.000Z","uid":293937,"like":10,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"55abd628087ef1878e9bf4358ad1e7e2ab95c5d9","tid":2432243,"uid":293937,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:28:46.000Z","msg":"【緬甸樞機主教：有如天安門！緬甸軍隊血腥鎮壓再創紀錄，單日釀38人亡】<br />\n<br />\n緬甸維安部隊今天對抗議者開火，聯合國緬甸事務特使柏其納表示共有38人喪生，是緬甸軍方上月發動政變後「最血腥」的一天。自緬甸軍方2月1日推翻文人領袖翁山蘇姬政府並拘禁她，終結緬甸十年來的民主實驗。隨後緬甸社會持續動盪，每天都有大型抗議。<br />\n<br />\n緬甸樞機主教薄茂恩在推特發文說，「我國的多數大城市有如天安門廣場」，他指的是中國1989年在北京殘酷鎮壓學生發起的抗爭。目擊者說，至今軍政府撲滅反政變抗議活動的決心似乎已增強，安全部隊在若干城鎮幾乎不加警告就對民眾發射實彈。社群媒體廣傳一段影音，畫面顯示&hellip;⬇️⬇️⬇️<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/s4Bim5F.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fs4Bim5F.jpg&h=5cfce51a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n聯合國：<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/mtvSrxv.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmtvSrxv.jpg&h=ed076ef6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b705b0dfbac0476f640c9a5f572e264991b7930d","tid":2432243,"uid":242537,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thumbs.gfycat.com/ColdFailingEsok-size_restricted.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthumbs.gfycat.com%2FColdFailingEsok-size_restricted.gif&h=92a8dfd6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f2c598a4bfea509d8a728b7369e7d4d02423da38","tid":2432243,"uid":31185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:00:21.000Z","msg":"Agger"},{"pid":"20f05aefc15c9988360d6d2ca8e988fe098f2580","tid":2432243,"uid":158613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-04T08:33:48.000Z","msg":"你想班老千仔點？自身難保<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}